description: [Afreximbank] Cairo, Egypt -- African Export-Import Bank (Afreximbank), Africa's leading multilateral financial institution, today marked a historic milestone with the groundbreaking ceremony of the Afreximbank African Trade Centre (AATC) in Egypt's New Capital, which will also be the home of the Bank's new global headquarters.
title: Africa: Afreximbank Breaks Ground On Its Iconic Trade Centre and New Headquarters in Egypt's New Capital

description: [Afreximbank] African Export-Import Bank (Afreximbank) has announced a donation of US$1.1 million to the governments of Jamaica and Haiti to support their recovery efforts following the devastation caused by Hurricane Melissa in October.
title: Africa: Afreximbank Announces U.S.$1.1- Million Donation to Aid Hurricane Melissa Recovery Efforts in Jamaica and Haiti
